    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Front Warning Lights</title>
        <para>The BE Series school bus is equipped with various warning light options as may required by both federal
            and state standards. The warning lights front and rear may also vary based on the requirements of the local
            school districts.
        </para>
        <figure id="f4700632" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg47/G4700632.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="312px"
                     scalefitheight="312px"/>
            <caption>Figure 32. Front Warning and Clearance Lights</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1>1. SIDE MARKER LIGHT (FEDERAL REQUIREMENT)</callout1>
                <callout1>2. AMBER FLASHING WARNING LIGHT (AS REQUIRED)</callout1>
                <callout1>3. RED FLASHING WARNING LIGHT (AS REQUIRED)</callout1>
                <callout1>4. AMBER CLEARANCE LIGHTS (FEDERAL STANDARD)</callout1>
                <callout1>5. IDENTIFICATION / DESTINATION SIGN (MAY BE LIGHTED)</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
    </svcsubproc>
